 First pitch is set for will make its College World Series debut on Friday, June 12, as it takes on Troy from Charles Schwab Field in Omaha, Nebraska. First pitch is scheduled for 7 p.m. ET.]]></description><media:thumbnail url="https://admin.wvusports.com/common/controls/image_handler.aspx?thumb_prefix=rp_system&amp;image_path=/images/2026/6/13/G1_Troy-211.jpg" /><media:content url="https://admin.wvusports.com/common/controls/image_handler.aspx?thumb_prefix=rp_primary&amp;image_path=/images/2026/6/13/G1_Troy-211.jpg"><media:title>Ian Korn, Paul Schoenfeld</media:title></media:content><enclosure url="https://admin.wvusports.com/common/controls/image_handler.aspx?thumb_prefix=rp_primary&amp;image_path=/images/2026/6/13/G1_Troy-211.jpg" length="1" type="image/jpg" /><pubDate>Sat, 13 Jun 2026 18:11:00 EST</pubDate><s:sport_id>1</s:sport_id><s:story_id>59192</s:story_id></item><item><title>Yehl, Kelly Pick Up Additional All-America Honors</title><link>https://wvusports.com/news/2026/6/13/baseball-yehl-kelly-pick-up-additional-all-america-honors</link><guid>https://wvusports.com/news/2026/6/13/baseball-yehl-kelly-pick-up-additional-all-america-honors</guid><category>Baseball</category><description><![CDATA[<img alt="Maxx Yehl, Gavin Kelly" src="https://admin.wvusports.com/common/controls/image_handler.aspx?thumb_prefix=rp_primary&image_path=/images/2026/6/13/Untitled-1Yehl__Kelly.jpg" /><br /><br />OMAHA, Neb. – Redshirt junior pitcher Maxx Yehl and sophomore catcher Gavin Kelly were both named All-Americans on Friday with Yehl earning a spot on the third team by the ABCA and Baseball America while Kelly was named to the second team by Baseball America.]]></description><media:thumbnail url="https://admin.wvusports.com/common/controls/image_handler.aspx?thumb_prefix=rp_system&amp;image_path=/images/2026/6/13/Untitled-1Yehl__Kelly.jpg" /><media:content url="https://admin.wvusports.com/common/controls/image_handler.aspx?thumb_prefix=rp_primary&amp;image_path=/images/2026/6/13/Untitled-1Yehl__Kelly.jpg"><media:title>Maxx Yehl, Gavin Kelly</media:title></media:content><enclosure url="https://admin.wvusports.com/common/controls/image_handler.aspx?thumb_prefix=rp_primary&amp;image_path=/images/2026/6/13/Untitled-1Yehl__Kelly.jpg" length="1" type="image/jpg" /><pubDate>Sat, 13 Jun 2026 10:46:00 EST</pubDate><s:sport_id>1</s:sport_id><s:story_id>59191</s:story_id></item></channel></rss>